author: MikaHolic Channel
text:
It was a very chaotic event to see (heck i watched it from Pekora, Miko, Subaru, Gura, Amelia, and AZKi's POVs simultaneously and my eyes were darting like crazy between those 6), but I enjoyed it very much.

Its quite sad that Aqua, Mio, Marine, Haachama and many others weren't able to participate in this event considering this is Coco's last Minecraft stream in Hololive...  But nonetheless everyone present made wonderful memories for Kaichou and for everyone. 

Thanks for the cute and fun antics, Rushia-chan!!

And to Coco... THANK YOU VERY, VERY MUCH!!!!
